2 days only, Friday 8 and Saturday 9 December. Don't miss out on these unprecedented opportunities, exclusively at Brisbane BMW and

Brisbane BMW 800 Ann Street, Fortitude Valley. Tel: 3853 0022. sales@brisbanebmw.com.au brisbanebmw.com.au

Licence 392387). Fees, charges, terms, conditions and approval criteria may apply. This is not an offer from BMW Financial Services. Cannot be combined with any other offer. Excludes fleet, govem ment and rental
buyers. See Brisbane BMW or Westside BMW for further details.
